WEBVTT

00:03.069 --> 00:04.570
<i>In the last episode of</i> Soap,

00:04.571 --> 00:06.071
<i>Elaine was shot, came home,</i>

00:06.072 --> 00:07.072
<i>and died.</i>

00:07.073 --> 00:09.575
<i>Eunice and Dutch, on a farm,</i>
<i>must hide.</i>

00:09.576 --> 00:11.577
<i>Burt told Mary he had an affair,</i>

00:11.578 --> 00:13.579
<i>but only because</i>
<i>she had one too,</i>

00:13.580 --> 00:16.081
<i>but Mary hadn't and told him so,</i>

00:16.082 --> 00:18.083
<i>and now Burt doesn't know</i>
<i>what to do.</i>

00:18.084 --> 00:20.085
<i>Burt and Mary talked,</i>

00:20.086 --> 00:22.588
<i>and then Jessica thinks</i>
<i>she loves two men.</i>

00:22.589 --> 00:25.090
<i>Confused? You don't know</i>
<i>what it's all about?</i>

00:25.091 --> 00:28.594
<i>Stay tuned tonight,</i>
<i>and you'll find out.</i>

